@startuml Sequence_Comment
title Sequence Diagram - Bình luận câu nghe (UC6)

actor User as U
participant "Lesson Page" as V
participant "CommentController" as CMC
participant "CommentService" as CMS
database "Database" as DB

== Tải danh sách Comment ==
U -> V : Xem trang Lesson, chọn Sentence
V -> CMC : GET /sentence/{id}/comments
CMC -> CMS : getTopLevelCommentsWithVotes(sentenceId)
CMS -> DB : SELECT c.* FROM comments c WHERE c.sentence_id = ? AND parent_id IS NULL
DB --> CMS : List<Comment>

loop Mỗi Comment
    CMS -> DB : countVotes(comment_id, true/false)
    DB --> CMS : likeCount, dislikeCount
    CMS -> CMS : populateVoteCounts
end

CMS -> CMS : Map thành DTO
CMS --> CMC : List<CommentDTO>
CMC --> V : Render comments
V --> U : Hiển thị comments với lượt vote

== Viết Comment mới ==
U -> V : Nhập nội dung comment
V -> CMC : POST /comment
CMC -> CMS : addComment(sentenceId, userId, content, null)
CMS -> DB : INSERT INTO comments\n(content, sentence_id, user_id,\nparent_id = NULL, created_at)
DB --> CMS : Saved Comment
CMS --> CMC : Comment
CMC --> V : Comment mới
V --> U : Hiển thị comment vừa tạo

== Reply Comment ==
U -> V : Nhấn Reply trên comment
U -> V : Nhập nội dung reply
V -> CMC : POST /comment
CMC -> CMS : addComment(sentenceId, userId, content, parentId)
CMS -> DB : INSERT INTO comments\n(content, sentence_id, user_id,\nparent_id = ?, created_at)
DB --> CMS : Saved Comment
CMS --> CMC : Reply Comment
CMC --> V : Reply mới
V --> U : Hiển thị reply dưới comment gốc

@enduml
